high_descs: Turn around and walk to the toilet on the right.
Pick up the sponge to the right of the candle on the back of the toilet.
Move to the other side of the room and face the sink.
Put the sponge inside the sink, rinse off the sponge with water, and pick it up from the sink.
Walk towards the door, take a right at the door and walk to the toilet.
Put the sponge on the back of the toilet in front of the other sponge.
anns.task_desc: To rinse off a sponge and put it on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and go forward to the wall, then turn right to face the toilet.
Pick up the leftmost sponge on the back of the toilet.
Turn right and go to the tub, then turn right and go to the wall, then turn right to face the sink.
Clean the sponge in the sink.
Go to the door in front of you, then turn right and go to the toilet up ahead.
Put the sponge on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn to the left twice, walk to the front of the toilet and turn right to face it.
Pick up the closest sponge on the toilet lid.
Turn to the right, move forward to the side of the sink and turn right to face it.
Wet the sponge in the sink.
Turn right, move to the door, turn right again and walk to the toilet.
Put the sponge on the toilet lid.
anns.task_desc: Wet a sponge from the toilet lid in the sink and return it.
